      "description" : "Overnight, Jay Chou, Leehom Wang, and David Tao set a gentle pace, with Ariana Grande and The Weeknd weaving in and out. Afternoon brought a full run of mandopop, K-pop, and R&B—no skips, just steady, familiar voices. 203 minutes, 52 tracks, 32 artists—a New Year’s Day anchored in your annual favorites.",
